title: Sizzling Hot Game v.1.0.0.8 (PC)
description:
The famous Sizzling Hot Game, now availbale for PC.

Download, extract and play. 

Requirements : Microsoft Visual Basic C++ 2005,2008,2010,2012 ; Net Framework and DirectX so that application runs.

Start cash 1000 euros, that is always when game starts. On a new game start previous balance not saved bur back to 1000 euros.

Do not change bet or do anything else, at least on the first 10 games.

Thank you to the german game developer!

Seed, share and enjoy!
